VignetteBuilder: knitr
Package: clusterMLD
Type: Package
Title: Cluster Multivariate Longitudinal Data
Version: 0.3.1
Author: Junyi Zhou
Maintainer: Junyi Zhou <junyzhou@iu.edu>
Description: This package is designed to cluster longitudinal data, especially for those data with sparse and irregular observations. 
    Besides, the algorithm is able to detect clusters with unbalanced size, i.e., some cluster sizes are outnumbered by the rests.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: stats, methods, splines, MASS, dplyr, utils, foreach, ggplot2, plotly
Suggests:
    roxygen2,
    knitr
Depends: 
     R (>= 3.6.0)
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
URL: https://github.com/junyzhou10/clusterMLD
